data.description: This custom home, built by a legendary Mayor of League City, is a one-of-a-kind find! From its spacious lawns, premium brick finish and wrought iron gate outside, to its vaulted ceilings, granite counters, and brick finishes inside, this home has classic good looks and an aristocratic feel. Designed for the perfect balance between generous entertaining and everyday living! With a cozy bedroom wing off to one side, the rest of the home boasts an open plan perfect for gathering with family and friends. The glass-walled family room overlooks the backyard terrace, creating the perfect setting for parties, BBQs or watching the kids play. Enjoy good times at the large pool that has an adjoining guest/pool house with a full bath and kitchen and would make a great home office! Nearby Interstate 45 makes a drive to shopping, beaches or downtown Houston, a breeze! Don't miss out on this rare opportunity to have the lifestyle you've always wished for!
